      <title>Promotion or Ads       on Whatsapp Channel Terms</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/ads/whatsapp-promotion/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Sep 2025 17:48:35 +0530</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/ads/whatsapp-promotion/</guid>
      <description>&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;&#xA;&lt;html lang=&#34;en&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;head&gt;&#xA;    &lt;meta charset=&#34;UTF-8&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;meta name=&#34;viewport&#34; content=&#34;width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;title&gt;Terms &amp; Conditions for WhatsApp Promotion&lt;/title&gt;&#xA;    &lt;link rel=&#34;stylesheet&#34; href=&#34;\css\wa-promotion.css&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;style&gt;&#xA;       &#xA;    &lt;/style&gt;&#xA;&lt;/head&gt;&#xA;&lt;body&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;terms-container&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;header class=&#34;terms-header&#34;&gt;&#xA;            &lt;h1&gt;Terms &amp; Conditions for WhatsApp Promotion&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/header&gt;&#xA;        &#xA;       &lt;div class=&#34;terms-section&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;div class=&#34;term-item&#34;&gt;&#xA;            &lt;h2&gt;1. Single Posting Rule:&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;            &lt;p&gt;We will post your content only once. If the post/link is correct, functional, and free from errors, it will neither be modified nor reposted again.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;        &lt;div class=&#34;term-item&#34;&gt;&#xA;            &lt;h2&gt;2. Posting Duration:&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;            &lt;p&gt;The post/link you provide will be shared on our channel for a fixed duration of 24-48 hours only.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;        &lt;div class=&#34;term-item&#34;&gt;&#xA;            &lt;h2&gt;3. Right to Update New Posts:&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;            &lt;p&gt;30 minutes after your post or link is shared, we reserve the right to update new posts on our channel.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
